{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-flex-grow-property-to-expand-items","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-flexbox","demoType":null,"title":"Koristi svojstvo `flex-grow` da proširiš element","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Suprotno od <code>flex-shrink</code> je svojstvo <code>flex-grow</code>. Zapamtite da <code>flex-shrink</code> kontroliše veličinu objekata kada kontejner raste. Svojstvo <code>flex-grow</code> kontroliše veličinu objekata kada roditeljski kontejner se širi.</p>\n<p>Koristeći primer kao onaj iz prošlog izazova, ako jedan element ima vrednost <code>flex-grow</code> od <code>1</code> a drugi ima vrednost <code>flex-grow</code> od <code>3</code>, onaj sa vrednošću <code>3</code> će biti tri puta veći od drugog.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d78ae367417b2b2512afc","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Povećajte svojstvo CSS <code>flex-grow</code> za <code>#box-1</code> na <code>#box-2</code>. Postavite <code>#box-1</code> na vrednost <code>1</code> i <code>#box-2</code> na vrednost <code>2</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/p/pVaDAv/c2p78cg","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301111,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-flex-grow-property-to-expand-items"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  #box-container {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    height: 500px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  #box-1 {\r\n    background-color: dodgerblue;\r\n    height: 200px;\r\n\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  #box-2 {\r\n    background-color: orangered;\r\n    height: 200px;\r\n\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"box-container\">\r\n  <div id=\"box-1\"></div>\r\n  <div i